{"tid":700670,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"全港台式飲品店黎講 「良辰吉時」 D靚妹靚仔應該係最好禮貌","createTime":"2018-06-13T13:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T15:05:33.000Z","uid":52539,"like":4,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8cefe71aadb061d88f65ec47755edd74693b3d8e","tid":700670,"uid":52539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日經過咁岩佢開門 野飲就一般般 要排既話一定唔買嫁喇<br />\n<br />\n買果時會望住你微笑 比足面<br />\n問佢有咩推介 仲慢慢笑住同我介紹 好好語氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一個打扮過既金髮MK妹 估唔到都好好笑容 <br />\n最驚喜係每個客拎果時 佢都會突然烏前少少個身 近距離望住你對眼講記得要搖一下佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係毒撚既話真係小D定力都唔掂比佢電暈<br />\n不過好彩我夠老煉 日日都有照鏡 自己知自己事 唔會FF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他仔仔既都OK好態度 不過冇另外兩個咁突出<br />\n估唔到依家D DSE雞咁得體<br />\n唔洗比貢茶/COMEBUY班仆街偽韓妹閪面"},{"pid":"efb6c6dc16c42563ee5fda8c19f387f45d079fde","tid":700670,"uid":132587,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:39:39.000Z","msg":"出一次呢d post收幾錢?"},{"pid":"231be8819558fb3bcd363eceaa625eed0520823c","tid":700670,"uid":52539,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"efb6c6dc16c42563ee5fda8c19f387f45d079fde","tid":700670,"uid":132587,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:39:39.000Z","msg":"出一次呢d post收幾錢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"洗鬼請打手咩 間野排到ON9<br />\n真係傻既先排 D野飲好一般 天仁10分既話佢得6~7分<br />\n<br />\n今日買唔到PS4特價$99GAME先去買炸 睇我另一個 POST屌柒PS HK &amp;屌柒貢茶妹就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7c72a46aec99355a78b94825879514eb2439c5","tid":700670,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T14:06:05.000Z","msg":"圖都無張，不孝子"},{"pid":"0f448ac403a7f97546f13cd5dd26fec6992162d4","tid":700670,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"毒撚到你"},{"pid":"8ee79298a79ff2